v0.1.0
======

	- Macro ESPACE_ERRDEC(): Declare ERROR
	- Macro ESPACE_ERRDEF(): Define ERROR
	- espace: ERROR_STATE
	- espace_raise(): Raise ERROR
	- espace_check(): Check ERROR
	- espace_catch(): Catch ERROR
	- espace_clear(): Clear ERROR
	- espace_perro(): Print ERROR_IDENTITY to stderr
	- sys_raise(): Raise System Error as ESPACE's ERROR
